[2026-05-02] FinanceBench page-level index + hybrid page rerank + evidence pack

Summary:
- Added page-level storage at upload time: each page now stores doc_name, filename, page_number, page_text, table_text, and chunk_ids.
- Kept stage-1 global chunk/doc retrieval, then switched stage-2 to page-level rerank inside selected docs.
- Page rerank now blends dense_score, BM25/keyword_score, number/year overlap, metric keyword overlap, and initial chunk hit signal.
- Built final LLM context as evidence pack entries with doc_name, filename, page_number, type, and text.
- Extended rag_trace with selected_docs, selected_pages, page_scores, and final_evidence_pack.

